data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF and check out the solar panels for electric savings! This spacious and meticulously maintained home at 3925 Agualinda Blvd in Cape Coral, Florida offers 4 bedrooms, a den/office, a formal dining room, and a great room, providing ample space for both family living and entertaining. The kitchen features white cabinets, granite countertops, a built-in pantry, and stainless steel appliances. Vaulted ceilings and white marble-like tile floors throughout create an open and airy ambiance. The large master suite offers two walk-in closets and an en-suite bathroom with a new walk-in shower, granite countertops, and dual sinks. The guest bathroom also boasts white cabinets and granite countertops. One of the standout features is the screened lanai with paver flooring, measuring 26 feet, offering a serene outdoor space. The expansive backyard provides room for a future pool. The home features a 2016-installed 16-seer A/C system, New Hybrid Energy Saving hot water heater (with heat pump), and 2018-installed 7.67kw roof-mounted solar panels for energy efficiency. This home, in a sought-after neighborhood, is the perfect place to call home and create lasting memories.
